h1 Helper

p  muffins by default contains some helper classes.

h2 Classes

h3 Floating 
p 
  | With the classes
  code .left
  | , 
  code .right
  |   and 
  code .clearfix
  |  elements can be positioned quickly and easily.

h6 Usage
pre
  code
    header HTML
    p
      = '<div class="clearfix">'
      br
      = '   <a class="btn primary left">.left</a>'
      br
      = '   <a class="btn primary right">.right</a>'
      br
      = '</div>'
h6 Output
.example
  .clearfix
    a.btn.primary.left = " .left"
    a.btn.primary.right= ".right"

